For those writing GI tests that involve the Ace Editor, here is an example on how to get and set text within the editor: https://app.ghostinspector.com/tests/5de9159f41fe8157e141d154
```// The following line grabs the ace editor
var editor = ace.edit("editor");

// Set some text
editor.setValue('my text here');

// Get the value within the editor
var aceValue = editor.getValue();```
